data.description: ONE OF A KIND GEM ON THE GOLF COURSE! Exceptional generous home featuring 5 bedrooms with 3 1/2 bathrooms. Spend the beautiful days on the balcony watching over the golf course. The minute you walk in the home, you feel the warm presence of tranquility with high decorative ceilings giving it the key touch to elegance. A big bonus to this home is that there is 2 master bedrooms, one upstairs and one downstairs. Come and see for yourself all this home entails. A MUST SEE!
